title: C-A-L-F
typeOfFood: Vegan, Western, Fast food, Take-out, Bakery, English
description: Must call ahead before you go as its hours change seasonally. Vegan cafe and takeaway est. Nov 2012. Offers a large range of food like bagels, hot meals, and sandwiches to starters and vegan desserts. Beverages include juices, shakes, hot chocolate, coffee and teas. All food is cooked on the premises by staff. Also has an area selling vegan groceries, shirts, and accessories. Profits go towards the upkeep of the C-A-L-F rescue animal sanctuary.
